subject: Re: Two Files That Will Explain Clipping
author: purplespacefriend
full_text:
I don't disagree with the explanation for clipping, and it sounded 
reasonable, but I think I would leave in the the hicups, I get those in 
normal boxes as well, I call it pre, and post echos, and the voices 
tend to repeat sometimes. So who's to say if it's actually a part of 
the voice?

 Frank-S
